trend_summary: Between earliest and latest scenes, scattered housing and farms expand gradually. Forest cover contracts as new clearings and low-density subdivisions appear, mainly along main roads and northeast edge. Agricultural fields enlarge and diversify. No large commercial cores emerge; landscape remains mostly rural with sparse, dispersed built-up footprint.
